high_descs: Turn around, then right and face the black couch on your left.
Take the credit card in the center from the black couch.
Turn right, then right again around the center table, then left and head to the green lamp in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Grab your credit card while turning on a lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the couch past the coffee table
Pick up the red credit card from the couch
Turn right and walk around the coffee table to the floor lamp in the corner
anns.task_desc: Examine the credit card under light of the floor lamp

high_descs: Turn around to walk towards the black couch and make a right walking between the couch and the table. Turn left to face the middle of the black couch.
Pick up the red credit card that is on the couch. Lift the card up under the lamp shade.
Turn right and go towards the chair then turn right past the chairs. Head left towards the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Take the credit card over to the lamp to turn it on.
